OL,3,CResidents cleared from their homes for
OL,4,Ctwo hours after police search home
OL,6,FPolice sealed off a Birmingham road
OL,7,Fand evacuated homes as 'suspicious
OL,8,Fitems' were found in a raid today.
OL,10,FResidents living in the Hollymoor Way
OL,11,Farea of Northfield were cleared for
OL,12,Faround two hours as a bomb squad,
OL,13,Ffirearms officers and police were
OL,14,Fspotted this afternoon, Saturday, May
OL,15,F9.
OL,17,FThe Army's EOD (Explosive Ordnance
OL,18,FDisposal) team was scrambled to the
OL,19,Fstreet as a "precaution" after the
OL,20,Fdiscoveries by West Midlands Police.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
