OL,3,CResidents cleared from their homes for
OL,4,Ctwo hours after police search home
OL,6,FThe road reopened shortly after 3pm
OL,7,Fand police later confirmed the items
OL,8,Ffound were "declared safe by the EOD."
OL,10,FPolice said the raid on a home in
OL,11,FHollymoor Way was part of an "ongoing
OL,12,Finvestigation".
OL,14,FA spokeswoman for West Midlands Police
OL,15,Fsaid: "As part of an ongoing
OL,16,Finvestigation, officers have today
OL,17,Fbeen carrying out a search at an
OL,18,Faddress on Hollymoor Way.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
