OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1778367998
OL,3,CResidents cleared from their homes for
OL,4,Ctwo hours after police search home
OL,6,F"This afternoon, a number of
OL,7,Fsuspicious items were found at the
OL,8,Faddress.
OL,10,F"As a result, the Army's EOD team have
OL,11,Fbeen called as a precaution. Officers
OL,12,Fremain at the scene this afternoon.
OL,14,F"As a precaution several homes have
OL,15,Fbeen evacuated while searches take
OL,16,Fplace."
OL,18,FSeveral marked police cars, along with
OL,19,Fa bomb disposal unit, were seen both
OL,20,Finside and outside the police cordon
OL,21,Fthis afternoon.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
