OL,3,CResidents cleared from their homes for
OL,4,Ctwo hours after police search home
OL,6,FOne nearby resident said: "We were
OL,7,Fjust told to evacuate. We've been out
OL,8,Fof our homes for around two hours, but
OL,9,Fnow we can go back in. It's all a bit
OL,10,Fstrange."
OL,12,FAnother resident said they thought a
OL,13,F"white ball of some kind" had been
OL,14,Ffound. It was unclear what that may
OL,15,Frefer to.
OL,17,FAt the time of the incident, a
OL,18,Fresident living in nearby Birch Avenue
OL,19,Fsaid: "Houses evacuated. All houses
OL,20,Fevacuated
